{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef272fec6d","title":"给康生的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b004821d1","index":0,"year":1962,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"ef272fec6d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"1c699c2030","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"康生，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央文教小组副组长。"},{"id":"a7e437fda2","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"郭沫若，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长、中国科学院院长。"},{"id":"d24b2ebd78","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指郭沫若1962年1月6日在广州作的七律：“赖有晴空露雷，不教白骨聚成堆。九天四海澄迷雾，八十一番大灾。借受折磨知悔恨，猪期振奋报清埃。金晴火眼无容救，哪怕妖精亿度来！”这是他读了毛泽东1961年11月17日作的《七律·和郭沫若同志》后写的。14]指毛泽东1961年12月作的《卜算子·咏梅》一词。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3923965b99","type":"title","text":"给康生\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"1c699c2030","type":"paragraph","text":"康生同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"a7e437fda2","type":"paragraph","text":"八日惠书收到，极高兴。请告郭沫若叫同志，他的和诗好，不要“千刀当刚唐僧肉”了，对中间派采取了统一战线政策，这就","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"d24b2ebd78","type":"subtitle","text":"好了。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"df48b77d70","type":"paragraph","text":"近作咏梅词一首，是反修正主义的，寄上请一阅。并请送沫若一阅。外附陆游咏梅词一首。末尾的说明是我作的，我想是这样的。究竟此词何年所作，主题是什么，尚有待于考证。我不过望文生义说几句黑了","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"6158de603a","type":"paragraph","text":"请代问郭老好！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"358c27a720","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"},{"id":"ccd48b7d0b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年一月十二日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d"}],"page":{"id":"440233bdd9","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"ef272fec6d","start":46,"end":46}}}},"__N_SSG":true}